column9: methodology: This dataset contains interaction data between characters in the  Star Wars prequal movies created by George Lucas. The links between characters are defined from when they are shown on screen. Multiple interaction types can happen between characters within a scene, signalling a new interaction for interaction types in the same scene. character1 and character2 are characters who are directly interacting with each other. These timestamps were derived from the DisneyPlus streaming service.
